📡 Packet Analysis with Wireshark
📌 Objective

To capture and analyze network traffic using Wireshark, identify protocols like HTTP, FTP, DNS, extract sensitive data from unencrypted traffic, and simulate a SYN flood attack for analysis.

🛠️ Tools Used
Wireshark
Kali Linux
hping3
Metasploitable2 (for FTP testing)
